title: Any1 on east coast noticing their MS is higher than normal?
body: I usually average at around 40-42 MS when I play LoL im in FL, currently sitting at 66-68 past few days. Any1 else noticing any differences in their MS?

replies.body:
Changes in latency are often caused by ISP routing changes that impact how long it takes for your connection to hit our servers. We can investigate into your route after you've confirmed your local network settings are aligned with our [network guide.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if your latency changed as a result of those steps.
